               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 5ra-135vb)
                     II) Maṣḥafa fǝlsatu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Translation of ʾabuna
                     Takla Haymanot” (136ra-147vb)
 III) Taʾammǝra Takla Hāymānot “Miracles of
                     Takla Haymanot”: 69 miracles (fols. 148ra-209vb)
 
 Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
